it is supposed to be sheer
it is very very popular in countries such as south korea and japan to have such minimal and soft looking makeup as it comes across as being more "cute" its very popular to use those colours as well as applying such a thin and small amount as they dont like going overboard with it. in my opinion, i really really like korean beauty and much prefer a more toned down and soft look.
